events.body:
`git bisect` points to f5bc018948f389559ccfaca128b07c9b17b3218b from https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/35182. Specifically, this line is the culprit: https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/f5bc018948f389559ccfaca128b07c9b17b3218b/src/test/util/setup_common.h#L16

This can be reproduced with the following patch on top of the master branch @ 08a25a7231341e7da54eae468d7411c2c85ced19:
```diff
--- a/src/test/util/setup_common.h
+++ b/src/test/util/setup_common.h
@@ -18,6 +18,7 @@
 #include <util/chaintype.h> // IWYU pragma: export
 #include <util/fs.h>
 #include <util/signalinterrupt.h>
+#include <util/sock.h>
 #include <util/vector.h>
 
 #include <cstddef>
```

